Azumi Says Automakers Are Main Engine for Economy of Japan

-- B y   T o r u   F u j i o k a
-- 
2011-12-09T17:46:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/azumi-says-automakers-are-main-engine-for-economy-of-japan.html
Japanese Finance Minister  Jun Azumi 
said automakers are the main engine for the economy after the
government decided to extend tax breaks for fuel-efficient cars.
Azumi spoke to reporters in  Tokyo  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Toru Fujioka in Tokyo at 
